(282, 1, '2019-01-24 19:59:04', '2019-01-24 19:59:04', '<!-- wp:html -->\nSuministro de&nbsp;<strong>lubricantes y agua potable.</strong>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'Que ofrecemos 2', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '25-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-24 19:59:04', '2019-01-24 19:59:04', '', 25, 'http://enermar.com.mx/cms/25-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(281, 1, '2019-01-24 19:58:43', '2019-01-24 19:58:43', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fluidos de perforación</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Que ofrecemos 4', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '33-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-24 19:58:43', '2019-01-24 19:58:43', '', 33, 'http://enermar.com.mx/cms/33-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(283, 1, '2019-01-24 19:59:52', '2019-01-24 19:59:52', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Somos capaces de cubrir sus requerimientos de combustible, lubricantes, agua potable, fluidos de perforación y logística marina.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ofrecemos el servicio integral de entrega offshore de combustible, que incluye desde cambio de guardia de personal hasta traslado de materiales a plataformas y embarcaciones.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'NUESTROS SERVICIOS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '56-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-24 19:59:52', '2019-01-24 19:59:52', '', 56, 'http://enermar.com.mx/cms/56-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(286, 1, '2019-01-24 20:01:48', '2019-01-24 20:01:48', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drilling fluids</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'What we offer 4', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '112-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-24 20:01:48', '2019-01-24 20:01:48', '', 112, 'http://enermar.com.mx/cms/112-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(285, 1, '2019-01-24 20:01:23', '2019-01-24 20:01:23', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are a company specialized in the <strong>distribution and trading of marine fuels for vessels, oil rigs and drilling fluid plants</strong> with a team highly trained and committed to always provide the best service in each supply, always facilitating the ideal operation of your operations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'ABOUT US', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '103-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-24 20:01:23', '2019-01-24 20:01:23', '', 103, 'http://enermar.com.mx/cms/103-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(303, 1, '2019-03-05 22:11:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 'Borrador automático', '', 'auto-draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2019-03-05 22:11:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://enermar.com.mx/cms/?p=303', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(288, 1, '2019-01-24 20:03:28', '2019-01-24 20:03:28', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are able to cover your fuel, lubricants, fresh water, drilling fluids and marine logistics requirements.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We offer the integral service of offshore fuel delivery, which includes everything from the change of personnel guard to the transfer of materials to platforms and vessels.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Our services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '127-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-24 20:03:28', '2019-01-24 20:03:28', '', 127, 'http://enermar.com.mx/cms/127-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
